import React from "react"
import EXIF from "../classes/EXIF"
import { connect } from "react-redux"
import { bindActionCreators } from "redux"
import { Camera, FACING_MODES } from "react-html5-camera-photo"

const IMG_DATA = "data:image/jpeg;base64,"

export interface PostProps {}

export class Post extends React.Component<PostProps, any> {
	render() {
		return (
			<div>
				<Camera
					idealFacingMode={FACING_MODES.ENVIRONMENT}
					onTakePhoto={(dataUri) => {
						let exif = new EXIF()
						let image = new Image()

						image.onload = function () {
							exif.getData(image, function () {
								console.log(exif.pretty(this))
							})
						}

						image.src = IMG_DATA
						console.log(dataUri)
					}}
				/>
				Î
			</div>
		)
	}
}

const PostDispatchToProps = (dispatch) => {
	return {
		// action: bindActionCreators(action, dispatch),
	}
}

export default connect(null, PostDispatchToProps)(Post)
